              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3z31p82x/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>forward to it with anxiety.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The recent triumph of Judaism in <placeName>England</placeName><lb/>\n                is looked upon by <persName>Dr Wise</persName> as another evidence<lb/> of the\n                emancipation of <placeName>Israel</placeName> and their growing<lb/> importance. He\n                says “this is another evidence<lb/> of the growing intelligence of mankind—our<lb/>\n                people are being redeemed from the Heralldom<add>?</add><lb/> of ages and in due\n                time willcome to be<lb/> regarded as the God of <placeName>Israel</placeName>\n                intended they<lb/> should be. They will be a <hi rend=\"underline\">nation of\n                    priests</hi> in<lb/> truth and will lead the world up to God<lb/> through the\n                faith of <persName>Abraham</persName> “&amp;c</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Pardon me for intruding at<lb/> such length upon your valuable time\n                with <del>by</del><lb/> my deultory correspondence and<lb/> with renewed wishes of\n                good health<lb/> believe me most truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">your friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B F. Peixotto</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear wife &amp; all your friends here<lb/> desire their affectionate regards.</p>\n            <p>I enclose a brief paragraph for publi-<lb/>cation (if not too late) in\n                    <date>Sept</date> No.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3z31p82x/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
